# рҹҡҖ JobPortal

Welcome to **JobPortal** вҖ” a full-stack job portal project with a Java Spring Boot backend and a React-based frontend.

---

## рҹ“Ң Project Overview

This project helps users:

- рҹ”Һ Browse available jobs
- рҹ§  Search jobs by keyword
- рҹ“қ Save job preferences
- рҹҺҜ Get tailored/recommended jobs
- вңҸпёҸ Edit existing job listings
- рҹ—‘пёҸ Delete jobs from the portal

It is split into two main parts:

- вҡҷпёҸ `job-backend` (Spring Boot REST API + MySQL)
- рҹҺЁ `job-frontend` (React via CDN + HTML/CSS/JS)

